        <p>Keep all your projects in one place. Sorted by projects you created as well as projects others have tagged you in, the main projects index page lets you organize your different projects with different teams to make sure you never have too much on your plate!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="product-features col-sm-4">
        <center><img class="img-circle img-responsive" src="assets/screenshots/tasks.png" alt=""></center>
