      </div>
      <div class="product-features col-sm-4">
        <center><img class="img-circle img-responsive" src="assets/screenshots/project_show.png" alt=""></center>
        <h2>Detailed Project Files</h2>
        <p>Keep track of your project with all the different features available. Upload images you want to share with your team members and they can view it right away. With tons of new features coming out with every update, managing your team will never be easier!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
